Title: CMC expands custom services attributes for Nagios plugins
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: cmc
Date: 1663850153
Edition: cee
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
State: unknown
Version: 2.1.0p13

For example, users may now define a custom service attribute
"PORT" in the global settings, set a value to this attribute
with a rule under "Custom service attributes", and use the
corresponding macro "$_SERVICEPORT$" under "Integrate
Nagios plugins".
